    <p><span>Sung Jinwoo's endless war begins anew.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Netmarble [39 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/netmarble">Netmarble</a> has announced <em><a title="Games > Solo Leveling: KARMA" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/solo-leveling-karma">Solo Leveling: KARMA</a></em>, a new <a title="Genres > Roguelite [263 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/roguelite">roguelite</a> <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,709 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a> based on the <em>Solo Leveling</em> intellectual property, coming to <a title="Platforms > PC [23,627 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, iOS, and Android. A release date and genre was not announced. <span id="more-977831"></span></p><p>“Sung Jinwoo enters the fray of an endless war once again!,” reads the teaser text. “We invite you to discover the untold tale of a 27-year gap. A tale never revealed in the original work.”</p><p>Watch the announcement trailer below. Visit the official website <a href="https://sololeveling-karma.netmarble.com/en/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p><h2><span>Announce Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="[Solo Leveling: KARMA] Exclusive Reveal Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GuK74T3ukhQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
